com.oracle.tools.runtime.java.virtualization
Class DelegatingMBeanServer

java.lang.Object
  com.oracle.tools.runtime.java.virtualization.DelegatingMBeanServer
All Implemented Interfaces:
MBeanServer, MBeanServerConnection
public class DelegatingMBeanServer
extends Object
implements MBeanServer

A DelegatingMBeanServer is an MBeanServer implementation that delegates calls to the appropriate MBeanServer of a VirtualizedSystem.
